    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1749732085\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Key Gameplay Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1️⃣ <strong>Drag and Drop:</strong> Place objects strategically to set the path for the bomb ball.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/7cb619be9bbe588d693ea5ffe22bf286.poster.avif?t=1749732085\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/7cb619be9bbe588d693ea5ffe22bf286.webm?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/7cb619be9bbe588d693ea5ffe22bf286.mp4?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2️⃣ <strong>Rotate and Position:</strong> Fine-tune your setup by rotating and placing objects in the perfect spot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/20df9be69c4fa4d06765d4a5c5d7ed81.poster.avif?t=1749732085\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/20df9be69c4fa4d06765d4a5c5d7ed81.webm?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/20df9be69c4fa4d06765d4a5c5d7ed81.mp4?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3️⃣ <strong>Aim and Shoot:</strong> Launch the bomb ball and watch it destroy the Marine's building.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/f2f71e29396f95745e67ea5a29aafb64.poster.avif?t=1749732085\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/f2f71e29396f95745e67ea5a29aafb64.webm?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266740/extras/f2f71e29396f95745e67ea5a29aafb64.mp4?t=1749732085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Pirates of Justice</strong> is an exciting puzzle game that challenges you to think strategically and solve problems to help pirates overthrow the corrupt Marine. In a world where the government protects a privileged few while disregarding the lives of ordinary people, it's up to you to fight for justice and dismantle the Marine's oppressive control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level tests your creativity and skills as you guide the pirate's bomb ball to destroy the Marine's buildings. With increasing difficulty and an engaging storyline of rebellion, Pirates of Justice offers a thrilling puzzle experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why Play Pirates of Justice?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Gameplay:</strong> Solve intricate puzzles by placing, rotating, and shooting objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Storyline:</strong> Rebel against injustice and fight for those the government abandoned.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progressive Challenges:</strong> Face increasingly complex puzzles as you rise through the pirate ranks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Level Design:</strong> Each level introduces unique obstacles to conquer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bounty System:</strong> Raise your pirate bounty with each victory and edge closer to becoming the King of the Pirates.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set sail on a journey of rebellion and strategy. <strong>Do you have what it takes to bring justice to the oppressed and earn your place in pirate history?</strong> Play <strong>Pirates of Justice</strong> now! </p>",
